data.description: Beautiful 3 bed 2 ba Glendale home. Versatile floor plan features separate living room and family. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space + pantry for storage, SS appliances, granite counters, and breakfast bar. Master suite with large closet, custom tile frameless glass shower, and updated vanity.  Generously sized secondary bedrooms + full guest bath w/ tile shower surround. The home features fresh neutral paint, tile flooring t/o w/ carpet in the bedrooms, and granite counters throughout. Private backyard w/ covered patio, grassy yard, and room for a pool! Dual RV gates w/ paved parking and NO HOA! Great location w/ no rear neighbors, close to schools, and easy freeway access
